WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.666 --> 00:00:02.333
I overheard a conversation

2
00:00:02.333 --> 00:00:04.433
between Duke Yuan and the consort in the Imperial Garden.

3
00:00:04.566 --> 00:00:07.200
Rest assured, I have already made arrangements.

4
00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:08.866
Princess Loulan will be the scapegoat.

5
00:00:08.866 --> 00:00:10.233
Loulan will surely incite public outrage.

6
00:00:10.666 --> 00:00:12.366
Even if they don't fight, they'll still cause a stir.

7
00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:16.166
When the chaos starts, you can add fuel to the fire in his harem.

8
00:00:16.166 --> 00:00:19.500
I don't believe I won't find an opportunity.

9
00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:20.700
That’s how things are.

10
00:00:20.700 --> 00:00:23.600
It’s a pity that I was the only one present at the time.

11
00:00:25.266 --> 00:00:27.300
If Your Majesty doesn’t believe it, I do.

12
00:00:30.600 --> 00:00:32.200
This concerns the consort.

13
00:00:32.566 --> 00:00:35.066
Your Majesty, shouldn’t you investigate further?

14
00:00:35.066 --> 00:00:36.300
No need to investigate further.

15
00:00:37.166 --> 00:00:39.500
I know best what kind of person the consort is.

16
00:00:39.600 --> 00:00:41.400
She’s capable of such things.

17
00:00:41.400 --> 00:00:43.966
Her reaction seems to indicate she was prepared.

18
00:00:44.366 --> 00:00:46.433
Then why was she still killed in her previous life?

19
00:00:46.466 --> 00:00:48.866
Could she have also been reborn?

20
00:00:48.933 --> 00:00:51.266
What does Your Majesty plan to do with them?

21
00:00:51.266 --> 00:00:53.700
After all, we don’t have substantial evidence.

22
00:00:53.700 --> 00:00:55.266
To prove she didn’t conspire?

23
00:00:55.400 --> 00:00:56.600
Who says there’s no evidence?

24
00:00:57.133 --> 00:00:59.766
I was only hesitant to scare the Empress Dowager before.

25
00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:01.666
Now that the Empress Dowager’s birthday banquet is over,

26
00:01:01.700 --> 00:01:03.933
we should properly settle accounts with them.

27
00:01:03.933 --> 00:01:05.466
Oh my God.

28
00:01:05.500 --> 00:01:07.600
This Emperor must really be reborn.

29
00:01:07.600 --> 00:01:09.766
Why has Consort Zhao’s rank dropped?

30
00:01:09.766 --> 00:01:13.166
In that case, appoint Su Xiu as the Consort Rong.

31
00:01:13.366 --> 00:01:15.100
Reside in Changchun Palace.

32
00:01:15.366 --> 00:01:18.400
Some things I can’t explain to you,

33
00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:19.466
but remember

34
00:01:19.466 --> 00:01:20.633
I am only playing a part

35
00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:22.433
with the consort.

36
00:01:22.800 --> 00:01:25.566
You’re right, you’re right.

37
00:01:25.933 --> 00:01:28.200
This dog Emperor is definitely reborn.
